700847f-a.title: Bronx: Dean Avenue - Layton Avenue
700847f-a.text:
Dean Ave., south of the S.W. corner of Layton Ave.
About 1927.
W. B. Vernan.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
700847f-a.folder: Dean Avenue & Layton Avenue, Bronx, NY

701397f-b.title: Bronx: Layton Avenue - Dean Avenue
701397f-b.text:
Layton Ave., hnorth side, east from Dean Ave., to its terminus on
Eastchester Bay.
July 17, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, at a later date, as seen from Shore Drive (one block
farther east). The Eureka Bathing Pavilion is at the N.E. corner
of the aforementioned thoroughfares.
August 25, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
